data.description: Welcome home! This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom is ready for a new owner! Situated in an established community, this home offers easy access to schools, parks, shopping, and commuter routes. Walk right into a sizeable living area with a cozy fireplace. First Floor Laundry and half bathroom. Spacious Kitchen with stainless steel appliances. Tons of natural light throughout. Large dining/flex area right off the kitchen. Upstairs you will find a full bathroom and 3 large rooms with great closet space. 3rd bedrooms boasts a walk-in closet. Lower Level is finished with 2nd Full Bathroom. Use your imagination here! Extra space to run around. Fenced in backyard, perfect for pets and children. Brand New Roof in 2023!
